        <Parent_String>equipment for grooming, hygiene and health care [300236656], personal equipment [300238982], equipment by context [300239170], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
